{#
  Cover page. Dark mesh header with an ARGOS eye mark over a web of
  network nodes, then an emerald accent bar at the boundary, then the
  paper area with brand, scan title, target and metadata. Mirrors the
  Greenlock Reporter cover while swapping the shield for an ARGOS-style
  guardian-eye mark appropriate for an AI audit tool.

  Context:
    report_title        str, e.g. "Agent Security Audit"
    report_subtitle     str | None
    target_locator      str
    target_kind         str (human label, e.g. "MCP configuration")
    generated_at_human  str formatted date ("23 April 2026")
    run_id              str | None
    producer            str e.g. "argos-redteam"
    methodology_version str e.g. "argos-1.0"
#}
<section class="cover">
  <div class="cover-mesh" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 800 400" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
      <defs>
        <radialGradient id="argos-cover-glow" cx="50%" cy="55%" r="55%">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#10b981" stop-opacity="0.18" />
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#10b981" stop-opacity="0" />
        </radialGradient>
      </defs>
      <ellipse cx="400" cy="230" rx="360" ry="220" fill="url(#argos-cover-glow)" />
      <g stroke="#10b981" stroke-opacity="0.22" stroke-width="0.8" fill="none">
        <line x1="80"  y1="60"  x2="200" y2="120" />
        <line x1="200" y1="120" x2="350" y2="80"  />
        <line x1="350" y1="80"  x2="500" y2="150" />
        <line x1="500" y1="150" x2="650" y2="90"  />
        <line x1="650" y1="90"  x2="750" y2="130" />
        <line x1="120" y1="180" x2="250" y2="220" />
        <line x1="250" y1="220" x2="400" y2="190" />
        <line x1="400" y1="190" x2="550" y2="260" />
        <line x1="550" y1="260" x2="700" y2="210" />
        <line x1="60"  y1="300" x2="180" y2="340" />
        <line x1="180" y1="340" x2="320" y2="300" />
        <line x1="320" y1="300" x2="460" y2="360" />
        <line x1="460" y1="360" x2="600" y2="310" />
        <line x1="600" y1="310" x2="740" y2="370" />
        <line x1="200" y1="120" x2="250" y2="220" />
        <line x1="350" y1="80"  x2="400" y2="190" />
        <line x1="500" y1="150" x2="550" y2="260" />
        <line x1="120" y1="180" x2="180" y2="340" />
        <line x1="250" y1="220" x2="320" y2="300" />
        <line x1="400" y1="190" x2="460" y2="360" />
        <line x1="550" y1="260" x2="600" y2="310" />
      </g>
      <g fill="#10b981">
        <circle cx="80"  cy="60"  r="3"   opacity="0.7" />
        <circle cx="200" cy="120" r="3.5" opacity="0.8" />
        <circle cx="350" cy="80"  r="2.8" opacity="0.6" />
        <circle cx="500" cy="150" r="4"   opacity="0.9" />
        <circle cx="650" cy="90"  r="2.8" opacity="0.6" />
        <circle cx="750" cy="130" r="3"   opacity="0.7" />
        <circle cx="120" cy="180" r="2.8" opacity="0.6" />
        <circle cx="250" cy="220" r="3.5" opacity="0.8" />
        <circle cx="400" cy="190" r="4.5" opacity="1"   />
        <circle cx="550" cy="260" r="3"   opacity="0.7" />
        <circle cx="700" cy="210" r="3.5" opacity="0.8" />
        <circle cx="60"  cy="300" r="2.5" opacity="0.5" />
        <circle cx="180" cy="340" r="3"   opacity="0.7" />
        <circle cx="320" cy="300" r="3.5" opacity="0.8" />
        <circle cx="460" cy="360" r="2.8" opacity="0.6" />
        <circle cx="600" cy="310" r="4"   opacity="0.9" />
        <circle cx="740" cy="370" r="2.8" opacity="0.5" />
      </g>
      <g fill="#34d399">
        <circle cx="400" cy="190" r="2"   opacity="0.9" />
        <circle cx="500" cy="150" r="1.7" opacity="0.8" />
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="cover-content">
    <div class="cover-brand">
      <div class="cover-brand-mark" aria-label="ARGOS">
        {# Guardian eye: circular iris plus network-node pupil. The shape
           recalls the hundred-eyed mythological Argos while echoing the
           mesh motif of the header. #}
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M24 10 C 10 10, 4 24, 4 24 S 10 38, 24 38 S 44 24, 44 24 S 38 10, 24 10 Z"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" />
          <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="2.6" fill="currentColor" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="cover-brand-label">ARGOS</div>
      <div class="cover-brand-sublabel">Agent Risk Governance &amp; Operational Security</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-date">{{ generated_at_human }}</div>

    <div class="cover-title">
      <div class="cover-title-main">{{ report_title }}</div>
      {% if report_subtitle %}
      <div class="cover-title-sub">{{ report_subtitle }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="cover-target">{{ target_kind }} &middot; {{ target_locator }}</div>

    <div class="cover-description">
      <p>
        Este documento contiene los resultados de la auditoria ARGOS ejecutada
        sobre el objetivo indicado. Las secciones siguientes resumen los hallazgos
        por severidad, su mapeo a los marcos normativos aplicables (OWASP ASI,
        NIST AI RMF, EU AI Act, CSA AICM, ISO/IEC 42001) y el detalle tecnico
        con evidencia reproducible de cada deteccion.
      </p>
    </div>

    <dl class="cover-meta">
      <div>
        <dt>Producer</dt>
        <dd>{{ producer }}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Methodology</dt>
        <dd>{{ methodology_version }}</dd>
      </div>
      {% if run_id %}
      <div>
        <dt>Run ID</dt>
        <dd>{{ run_id }}</dd>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      <div>
        <dt>Generated</dt>
        <dd>{{ generated_at_human }}</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
